data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLERS!! 
Located in the heart of Springtown with wonderful schools. There are two ways to enter the property, front on Main and back on N Avenue A. 
Home is being sold as is. This 3 bedroom 1 bath has potential for ALL buyers. It would be a great opportunity for investors, renovators, downsizing, and first-time homeowners with a vision. 
The lot is a large .33 acres and has 2 sheds (10x16 and 7x8), so much to offer in this home. 
Zoned residential but the property has the potential to be changed to commercial. Bring your buyers!
